Class NFC2WithLimit

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ForwardChecking, Profilable

    public class NFC2WithLimit
extends NFC2
implements ForwardChecking
    NFC2 is a ForwardChecking implementation for HyperGraph with immediate local propagation in one step. It maintain a list of possible candidats for each variables but only if the number of candidats in lower than a specified limit.

      NFC2WithLimit(int limit) 
      NFC2WithLimit(int limit, boolean enableCheckMode)
